node.text: Peacing out on the gram for a little ✌🏼 going to snuggle my babies, start a book, & enjoy the last few days of summer time! Can’t serve you all without taking care of me. I did want to leave y’all with rounding up some of my @nordstrom finds I’ve worn this month! #nordstrom #nordstrompartner #liketkit @shop.LTK http://liketk.it/3lUK4

node.text: Had the best time celebrating our girl all weekend. Truly thank you for all the love & messages - best IG aunties 🌈🦄 I’ve been so excited to share this dress with you all from @vicidolls (25% off with code dede25 today) #littlemissrosieraad #birthday #vicidolls #sunday #weekend

node.text: To our Rosie girl, you came at the best time for my mama heart when loosing my own & it’s been the greatest most challenging role yet. I’m not ready for 2 but excited to do this together with all that life throws our way bc currently YOU IS CRAZY 😜 can’t wait to celebrate you all weekend! Happy second baby girl! Sweater @pinklily

node.text: We blinked & now have a kid in school..will I ever be ready?! Met Rosie girl’s sweet teachers tonight.
